network.param.modules.catalogue

Class Catalogue

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.param.modules.catalogue.Catalogue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBean, ICatalogue

    public final class Catalogue
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICatalogue
    Implementation of ICatalogue, this class represents the Param Catalogue information.

    This interface ICatalogue will represents name, description, barcode, hsn code.., ICatalogue defines below categories of operations:

    • setTxType method to set TxnMode, By default it will set as Private mode

    • setName method to set name of the catalog.

    • setDescription method to set catalogue description.

    • getDescription method for get the catalogue description.

    • setInternalID method to set catalog internalID.

    • getInternalID method get the catalogue internal ID

    • setCategories method set parent and child category

    • getParentCategory method for get the parent category

    • setID method for set catalogue blockchain ID

    • getID method for get catalogue blockchain ID

    • getPurpose method for get catalogue catalogue purpose.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
